    CR -->|create, update, list| ConfigMaps
    CR -->|full CRUD| Events
    CR -->|full CRUD| PyTorchJobs
    CR -->|status updates| PyTorchJobsStatus
    CR -->|finalizers| PyTorchJobsFinalizers
    CR -->|full CRUD| TFJobs
    CR -->|status updates| TFJobsStatus
    CR -->|full CRUD| MPIJobs
    CR -->|status updates| MPIJobsStatus
    CR -->|full CRUD| XGBoostJobs
    CR -->|full CRUD| PaddleJobs
    CR -->|full CRUD| JAXJobs
    CR -->|full CRUD| HPA
    CR -->|full CRUD| VolcanoPodGroups
    CR -->|full CRUD| SchedPluginsPodGroups
    CR -->|full CRUD| NetworkPolicies
    CR -->|create, update| RolesAPI
    CR -->|create, update| RoleBindingsAPI
    CR -->|read, update| ValidatingWebhooks

    %% Role permissions (namespace-scoped)
    R -->|get, create, update| Secrets

